OL,5, One of the alleged masterminds and     
OL,6, financiers of the 1994 Rwandan genocide
OL,7, has gone on trial at a UN tribunal in  
OL,8, The Hague.                             
OL,10,FProsecutors say Felicien Kabuga aided  
OL,11,Fand abetted hit squads in the slaughter
OL,12,Fof ethnic Tutsis, and of using a radio 
OL,13,Fstation to incite hatred against them. 
OL,15,FSome 800,000 Tutsis and moderate Hutus 
OL,16,Fwere killed in the genocide.           
OL,18,FMr Kabuga's lawyers have filed a not   
OL,19,Fguilty plea for him but he has refused 
OL,20,Fto attend the opening of the trial.    
